hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Where's the postbox? donde comprar ginseng natural Flint and friends head back there, of course, dropped into a jungle setting that echoes “Jurassic Park,” with majestic shots of grazing scallion-brontos, close calls with a spidery cheeseburger, and “awww”-inspiring looks at a cutesy strawberry. Nicely designed, but shades of the exotica in “The Croods.” And “The Lorax.” And the Candyland riff in “Wreck-It Ralph.” And, funny coincidence, just as the “Jurassic” franchise has insisted on sending characters back to danger isle without any compelling reason, it’s the same here. Some contrived conflict between Flint and his loved ones doesn’t help recapture the first installment’s narrative ease, either.
